er":{"id":363837,"username":"zeke222","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zeke222","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40848142f8ee231e050ff9b50c2dda08?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40848142f8ee231e050ff9b50c2dda08?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/40848142f8ee231e050ff9b50c2dda08?s=73&d=retro","created":1542455590,"last_modified":1695525477},"last_reply_by":"blufaux","last_touched":1695529006,"title":"已关闭充电优化， iPhone 15 pro 充电只能到 80％+","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/976631","created":1695525706,"deleted":0,"content":"重启、强制重启以及换了充电头和线也都没办法解决。\r\n并且 80%+之后虽然电量上不去，在没有使用手机的情况下，手机温度还是比较高。\r\n并且重启前电量显示 81 或 82 ，重启后显示 84 或 85 。\r\n有人遇到了同样的情况吗？","content_rendered":"重启、强制重启以及换了充电头和线也都没办法解决。<br />并且 80%+之后虽然电量上不去，在没有使用手机的情况下，手机温度还是比较高。<br />并且重启前电量显示 81 或 82 ，重启后显示 84 或 85 。<br />有人遇到了同样的情况吗？","last_modified":1695525706,"replies":10,"id":976631},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":13624,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161","stars":6718,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":523373,"username":"reallittoma","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/reallittoma","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7dd5f45b84e616b2680cedd87d3838fc?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7dd5f45b84e616b2680cedd87d3838fc?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7dd5f45b84e616b2680cedd87d3838fc?s=73&d=retro","created":1607670874,"last_modified":1639707689},"last_reply_by":"CrazyRundong","last_touched":1695535548,"title":"家装 AC+AP，怎样优雅地使用 UU 加速器？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/976617","created":1695522426,"deleted":0,"content":"房子准备装修，正在考虑装 AC+AP 。由于家里都是重度主机玩家（主要是 Splatoon ），UU 加速器成了必需品。\r\n目前出租屋里用的是小米路由器，自带 UU 插件，主机只要连上网就能在手机客户端设置加速。\r\n我看了一下 UU 的支持列表（  https://uu.163.com/router/ ），似乎并没有 ACAP 的支持。\r\n\r\n* 如果用 PC 客户端加速，最多只能同时加速一台主机，而我至少需要两台同时加速。\r\n* 如果用 UU 盒子加速，可以同时加速两台主机，但小盒子的信号强度有限，挪来挪去也不方便，而且挂一个盒子在外面也不好看\r\n\r\n想请教一下大家，有没有比较优雅的解决办法？还是说如果非要用加速器，只能放弃 AC+AP 的方案？","content_rendered":"<p>房子准备装修，正在考虑装 AC+AP 。由于家里都是重度主机玩家（主要是 Splatoon ），UU 加速器成了必需品。\n目前出租屋里用的是小米路由器，自带 UU 插件，主机只要连上网就能在手机客户端设置加速。\n我看了一下 UU 的支持列表（  <a href=\"https://uu.163.com/router/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://uu.163.com/router/</a> ），似乎并没有 ACAP 的支持。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果用 PC 客户端加速，最多只能同时加速一台主机，而我至少需要两台同时加速。</li>\n<li>如果用 UU 盒子加速，可以同时加速两台主机，但小盒子的信号强度有限，挪来挪去也不方便，而且挂一个盒子在外面也不好看</li>\n</ul>\n<p>想请教一下大家，有没有比较优雅的解决办法？还是说如果非要用加速器，只能放弃 AC+AP 的方案？</p>\n","last_modified":1695522457,"replies":10,"id":976617},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":23624,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2712,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":90818,"username":"panlatent","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/panlatent","website":"https://panlatent.com","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"panlatent","btc":"","location":"北京","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d30b/8fb4/90818_mini.png?m=1663317782","av