one","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":10509,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":"iPhone","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","stars":3198,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":8,"parent_node_name":"apple"},"member":{"id":35980,"username":"shenyuzhi","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shenyuzhi","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d626/dd0e/35980_mini.png?m=1694068788","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d626/dd0e/35980_normal.png?m=1694068788","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d626/dd0e/35980_large.png?m=1694068788","created":1363423893,"last_modified":1694068788},"last_reply_by":"panlatent","last_touched":1695533403,"title":"蜂窝信号消失会导致 WiFi 密码错误","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/976652","created":1695530759,"deleted":0,"content":"一个持续了两年，非常烦的问题。\r\n\r\n我这边房子里蜂窝信号差，时有时无，所以比较依赖 WiFi 。\r\n\r\n一旦蜂窝信号消失，iPhone 手机的 WiFi 有可能同时消失，直接断网。此时如果手动连接那个 WiFi ，会提示密码错误。必须重启，不然再也连不了这个 WiFi 了。重启会自动连上该 WiFi 。\r\n\r\n我和我老婆的 iPhone 都有这个问题，她的 iPad （无蜂窝）偶尔也这样。其它的设备，包括数台 MacBook ，安卓手机，Windows 电脑，都是正常的。\r\n\r\n不知道有没有人有同样的问题，怎么解决。","content_rendered":"一个持续了两年，非常烦的问题。<br /><br />我这边房子里蜂窝信号差，时有时无，所以比较依赖 WiFi 。<br /><br />一旦蜂窝信号消失，iPhone 手机的 WiFi 有可能同时消失，直接断网。此时如果手动连接那个 WiFi ，会提示密码错误。必须重启，不然再也连不了这个 WiFi 了。重启会自动连上该 WiFi 。<br /><br />我和我老婆的 iPhone 都有这个问题，她的 iPad （无蜂窝）偶尔也这样。其它的设备，包括数台 MacBook ，安卓手机，Windows 电脑，都是正常的。<br /><br />不知道有没有人有同样的问题，怎么解决。","last_modified":1695530759,"replies":6,"id":976652},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":211232,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar